  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张图，说明注释数据是怎么从扫描阶段一路传递到最终AST节点的。核心问题是：同一条注释在Scanner、Parser、Composer三个模块里形态都不一样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCANNER",
        "PARSER",
        "COMPOSER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以重点是注释的流动，而不是词法分析本身。我先把三个子图搭出来：Scanner、Parser、Composer。每个里面放关键的处理节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCANNER",
        "PARSER",
        "COMPOSER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Scanner那边要区分两种扫描入口：一种是行尾注释，一种是块头块尾的注释。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我在Scanner里放了S1和S2，分别叫scanLineComment和scanComments。然后它们都输出到同一个Comment结构体？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，S3就是Comment struct，里面三个字段：head、line、foot，用来分类存放。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S3",
        "fields"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Parser这边我想到三个关键步骤：先把注释展开关联到token位置，然后存到Parser自己的字段里，最后转移到Event。需要把P4那个特殊事件也标出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，P4是TAIL_COMMENT_EVENT，专门处理块结尾的foot注释，这个容易漏掉。P1到P2是展开，P2到P3是常规转移，P2到P4是特殊出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4",
        "TAIL_COMMENT_EVENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连线画好了。Composer这边相对简单？我看到代码里node和mapping都有注释处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
