    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不简单，C2的mapping有重新赋值逻辑，和C1的node直接透传不一样。但两者最终都写到C3的Node字段里。",
      "elements_involved": [
