      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解，C1和C2都指向C3，但处理逻辑不同。现在跨模块的连线：S3到P1，P3到C1，P4到C2，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
